OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry evening
OL,6,Fwith some clearer spells, mainly in
OL,7,Fthe south. A band of thicker cloud
OL,8,Fwill spread south overnight, perhaps
OL,9,Fwith brief light rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAny early cloud will break
OL,12,Fto sunny spells, before further cloud
OL,13,Fspreads south through the morning,
OL,14,Fperhaps bringing a few showers. Most
OL,15,Fparts staying dry and warm. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
